OL,3,CFishing boat should have given way
OL,4,Cbefore deadly collision, defendant says
OL,6,FThe L'Ecume II vessel should have
OL,7,Fgiven way to the Commodore Goodwill
OL,8,FCondor Ferry before the deadly
OL,9,Fcollision which killed three
OL,10,Ffishermen, defendant Lewis Peter Carr
OL,11,Fhas told Jersey's Royal Court.
OL,13,FThe Condor employee, along with
OL,14,Fcolleague Artur Sevash-Zade, is on
OL,15,Ftrial for triple manslaughter
OL,16,Ffollowing the incident in December
OL,17,F2022 - they both deny all the charges.
