OL,3,CFishing boat should have given way
OL,4,Cbefore deadly collision, defendant says
OL,6,FMr Carr explained this was not to
OL,7,Favoid a collision, but instead to
OL,8,Fensure that the ferry would not go
OL,9,Finto the shallow waters near Corbiere
OL,10,F- off Jersey's south west coast.
OL,12,FHe added that the L'Ecume II was not
OL,13,Fdisplaying fishing lights, so it was
OL,14,Fclearly not engaged in fishing and
OL,15,Fshould have yielded to the ferry as it
OL,16,Fwas on portside.
